Plywood production, imports, exports, and consumption, by softwoods and hardwoods, 1950-87

Dataset containing various statistics for plywood products. (3/8-inch basis) All units are in Million Square ft unless otherwise specified. Year 1987 includes small volumes of mixed species (not classified as softwoods or hardwoods).

ulrich36

Format

A data frame with 38 observations of 15 variables:

Prod.Tot
Total Plywood Production
Prod.SW
Softwood Plywood Production
Prod.HW
Hardwood Plywood Production
Imports.Tot
Total Plywood Imports
Imports.SW
Softwood Plywood Imports
Imports.HW
Hardwood Plywood Imports
Exports.Tot
Total Plywood Exports
Exports.SW
Softwood Plywood Exports
Exports.HW
Hardwood Plywood Exports
Consump.Tot
Total Plywood Consumption
Consump.SW
Softwood Plywood Consumption
Consump.HW
Hardwood Plywood Consumption
PerCapitaConsump.Tot
Total Plywood Consumption Per Capita, in Square ft.
PerCapitaConsump.SW
Softwood Plywood Consumption Per Capita, in Square ft.
PerCapitaConsump.HW
Hardwood Plywood Consumption Per Capita, in Square ft.

U.S. Department of Commerce, Bureauot Census (40,50.51,52) American Plywood Association (5).
